Hi Team,

Can we use .net Standard Class Library Custom DataAnnotation in Xamarin.Forms for validation?

**.net Standard Class Library**

[DbRequired]
[Display(Name = "USER NAME", Prompt = "ENTER USER NAME")]
public string User_Name
{
get { return GetValue(() => User_Name); }
set { SetValue(() => User_Name, value); }
}

    [Display(Name = "PASSWORD", Prompt = "ENTER PASSWORD")]
    [DataType(DataType.Password)]
    [DbRequired]
    public string User_Password
    {
        get { return GetValue(() => User_Password); }
        set { SetValue(() => User_Password, value); }
    }

Please help us to use and validate from class library.
